data.description: NEW ROOF TO BE INSTALLED PRIOR TO CLOSING!  NO CDD!  LOW HOA FEES!  Adorable 3 bedroom, 2 bath home located in the popular Brandon Brook community.  You will love the vaulted ceilings that provide an open and spacious feel and all of the natural light that floods into this sweet home.  The split floor plan provides privacy and the beautiful easy-care luxury vinyl flooring that flows throughout the home connects each space seamlessly together.  Step out through the sliders off of the dining room into the fully fenced back yard, a great place for the pets and little ones to safely romp and play.  The master suite has ample space and will easily accommodate all your bedroom furniture.  The large walk-in closet is a definite plus! The living and dining spaces are open making entertaining friends and family comfortable and convenient.  The washer, dryer and hot water tank are all newer.  Brandon Brook is convenient to Hwy 60 with convenient access to I-4, I-75 and the Crosstown.  Shopping is close and convenient and all your favorites restaurants are just minutes away.  Make your appointment soon to view this charming home that is move-in ready and waiting for its new family!
